00:03:53.510 --> 00:03:57.510
Tip 1, make your conversation
as simple as possible,

00:03:57.510 --> 00:03:59.510
but no simpler.

00:03:59.510 --> 00:04:02.210
Do you know someone
who talks too much?

00:04:02.210 --> 00:04:05.000
Well, an action can too.

00:04:05.000 --> 00:04:08.390
When users interact,
keep it simple.

00:04:08.390 --> 00:04:11.210
Users don't need
every option up front.

00:04:11.210 --> 00:04:13.640
Guide them to the
most used portion,

00:04:13.640 --> 00:04:17.180
and then make options
available if they asked.

00:04:17.180 --> 00:04:20.480
Now, we're going to
