00:19:30.982 --> 00:19:32.440
A great way to
include a little bit

00:19:32.440 --> 00:19:35.320
of media inside of your action.

00:19:35.320 --> 00:19:37.360
Using the API is
straightforward.

00:19:37.360 --> 00:19:41.380
Just give the URL to an audio
file, titles, some images,

00:19:41.380 --> 00:19:44.492
and then hand it to Actions
on Google to play the rest.

00:19:44.492 --> 00:19:46.950
It's a great way to bring your
audio content to your users.

