00:21:42.681 --> 00:21:44.180
SUNIL VEMURI: All
right, what we did

00:21:44.180 --> 00:21:49.520
here is use two features
of SSML, par and prosody.

00:21:49.520 --> 00:21:51.950
Prosody lets you fine
tune how the computer

00:21:51.950 --> 00:21:56.810
speaks by changing the pitch,
speaking rate, and volume.

00:21:56.810 --> 00:21:59.630
Par is something unique
to Actions on Google.

00:21:59.630 --> 00:22:02.840
It lets you play multiple
