00:22:02.840 --> 00:22:06.500
sound effects, background audio,
and mix that with your text

00:22:06.500 --> 00:22:07.700
to speech.

00:22:07.700 --> 00:22:09.830
With that, you can
make great sounds

00:22:09.830 --> 00:22:11.270
in an atmosphere
for your action.

00:22:14.910 --> 00:22:18.000
To further help you make
a great audio environment

00:22:18.000 --> 00:22:22.030
for your sound, we have a sound
library with over 1,000 sounds,

00:22:22.030 --> 00:22:26.550
including ambient sounds,
